    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作需要您扮演一团成精的石油，从油业集团的围追堵截中逃出法网。游戏流程短小精悍但氛围感十足，绝对百玩不厌，快来体验这场妙趣横生的沙雕冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/52be4e3abea50c25e2a9a838fa64d27f.poster.avif?t=1770754034\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/52be4e3abea50c25e2a9a838fa64d27f.webm?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/52be4e3abea50c25e2a9a838fa64d27f.mp4?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹跳又乱撞</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为一坨师承马里奥的超级肥油，您自然轻功盖世，什么蹬墙反弹、创翻桶阵、油池打滑等等操作不过小菜一碟。操纵时间流速方显您的真正风采，在慢放中秀出一把神操作，好好欣赏您那花样繁多的身段！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/89f716c4e6cea81ec48c034462e6ae34.poster.avif?t=1770754034\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/89f716c4e6cea81ec48c034462e6ae34.webm?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/89f716c4e6cea81ec48c034462e6ae34.mp4?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >随地大小变</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >吞吐油滴调大小——吞吞吞变巨无霸横冲直撞，吐吐吐缩成油渍低调躲人。换上各种骚帽子，还能解锁限时超能力！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/b5213da178802367b8004705d9cf1938.poster.avif?t=1770754034\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/b5213da178802367b8004705d9cf1938.webm?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/b5213da178802367b8004705d9cf1938.mp4?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >刺激逃亡路</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开上叉车就是爽，谁敢拦路我搬谁！嘿，谁家机器人这么没礼貌？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/b55c2dba431c0ef6ee8f7f7d2db9bfd4.poster.avif?t=1770754034\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/b55c2dba431c0ef6ee8f7f7d2db9bfd4.webm?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262980/extras/b55c2dba431c0ef6ee8f7f7d2db9bfd4.mp4?t=1770754034\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Body Meat 爆肝配乐！</p>",
